# Package Map — Hana CMS Monorepo

> **Khi thêm/xoá package, plugin, hoặc app → cập nhật file này ngay.**

## Packages (`packages/`)

| Package | Npm scope | Mô tả | Được import bởi |
|---|---|---|---|
| `packages/hanano` | `hanano` | **Umbrella package** — re-export từ tất cả `@hanano/*` core, include admin dist, expose CLI bin `hanano` | end-users |
| `packages/types` | `@hanano/types` | TypeScript interfaces/types ONLY — không có runtime logic | Tất cả packages, plugins, apps |
| `packages/validator` | `@hanano/validator` | Zod schemas cho content, user, media, plugin | `@hanano/core`, plugins, admin |
| `packages/schema` | `@hanano/schema` | Drizzle base tables (`users`, `sessions`, `installed_plugins`, `media_files`), `mergeSchemas()` helper | `@hanano/core`, plugins |
| `packages/core` | `@hanano/core` | `HanaCMS` class, `HookRegistry`, `createDatabase()`, `LocalStorageAdapter`, core media routes (`/api/media`), static admin serve | plugins, apps, CLI |
| `packages/registry` | `@hanano/registry` | `PluginRegistryClient` — fetch plugin list, install/uninstall, verify SHA-256 integrity | `@hanano/core`, `@hanano/ui` |
| `packages/ui` | `@hanano/ui` | Vue `ComponentRegistry`, `themeWidgetRegistry` (theme extension widgets by slot), base components, Plugin Marketplace UI | `apps/admin`, plugins |
| `packages/cli` | `@hanano/cli` | CLI commands: `hanano init`, `hanano db push/generate/migrate`, `hanano plugin install/uninstall`. **Private** — exposed via `hanano` bin, không publish riêng | standalone binary |
| `packages/config` | `@hanano/config` | Shared tsconfig (`tsconfig.base.json`, `tsconfig.app.json`, `tsconfig.lib.json`). **Private** | Tất cả packages |

## Plugins (`plugins/`)

> Plugins là **Official plugins** — npm packages, cần `bun add` + restart.
> Khác với Community plugins (CDN bundle, dynamic import không cần restart).

| Plugin | Npm package | Tính năng |
|---|---|---|
| `plugins/plugin-auth` | `hanano-plugin-auth` | Schema + routes cho authentication (đăng ký, đăng nhập, sessions) |
| `plugins/plugin-blog` | `hanano-plugin-blog` | Posts/categories schema + CRUD REST routes + admin views (PostsView, CategoriesView) |
| `plugins/plugin-menu` | `hanano-plugin-menu` | Menu management — schema + CRUD REST routes + admin view (MenusView). Injects `menuMain`/`menuFooter` into theme context via `theme:beforeRender` hook |
| `plugins/plugin-pages` | `hanano-plugin-pages` | Standalone pages schema + CRUD routes, `theme:beforeRender` data injection + admin view (PagesView) |

## Themes (`themes/`)

> Themes là **built-in default themes** — đã đăng ký sẵn trong registry, user dùng ngay không cần cài thêm.
> Một thời điểm chỉ có 1 theme active, nhưng registry giữ nhiều themes để hot-swap.

| Theme | Npm package | Mô tả |
|---|---|---|
| `themes/theme-blog` | `hanano-theme-blog` | Blog theme — Eta templates, settings schema, static assets. Factory `blogTheme()` |
| `themes/theme-insurance` | `hanano-theme-insurance` | Insurance product theme — Eta templates (home/category/post/404), companion plugin for home carousel, full settings schema. Factory `insuranceTheme()` |

## Apps (`apps/`)

| App | Filter name | Mô tả | Port mặc định |
|---|---|---|---|
| `apps/admin` | `@hanano/admin` | Vue 3 SPA admin dashboard, build output embed vào `core/dist/admin` | 5173 (dev) |
| `apps/docs` | `@hanano/docs` | VitePress documentation site | 5174 |
| `apps/starter` | `@hanano/starter` | Template project cho end-users clone | — |

## Theme System

> Theme là **presentation abstraction** — tách biệt hoàn toàn với Plugin.
> Chi tiết contract xem `08-theme-api-contract.mdc`.

- Theme chịu trách nhiệm cho layout, styling, và template rendering (Eta).
- Một thời điểm chỉ có **đúng 1 theme active**.
- Theme **không** đăng ký routes hay schema tables riêng — chỉ cung cấp `.eta` templates, static assets, và optional `data()` hook.
- Types cho theme nằm trong `@hanano/types`, persistence trong `@hanano/schema`, runtime mounting trong `@hanano/core`.
- `CMSConfig.themes[]` đăng ký nhiều theme; `CMSConfig.defaultTheme` chỉ định fallback.
- Hot-swap: activate theme khác qua admin API không cần restart server.

## Entry Points Quan Trọng

```
packages/core/src/hana-cms.ts       → HanaCMS class, createCMS(), theme registry, hot-swap, companion plugin toggle, plugin-manifest + bundle-serving APIs
packages/core/src/hook-registry.ts  → HookRegistry class, runWaterfallAt()
packages/core/src/plugin-route-registry.ts → PluginRouteRegistry, plugin hot-swap middleware
packages/core/src/theme-runtime.ts  → ThemeRuntime, Eta template rendering
packages/core/src/database.ts       → createDatabase() (bun:sql + drizzle-orm/bun-sql)
packages/cli/src/commands/db.ts     → hanabi db push/generate/migrate (dynamic schema discovery + drizzle-kit)
packages/types/src/plugin.ts        → CMSPlugin, PluginAdminConfig, PluginAdminMenuItem, PluginLifecycle, CMSPluginHooks
packages/types/src/cms.ts           → CMSConfig (themes[], defaultTheme), DatabaseConfig, AdminConfig
packages/types/src/theme.ts         → CMSTheme (companionPlugin, routePattern), ThemeLayoutEntry
packages/schema/src/schema-builder.ts → mergeSchemas()
packages/registry/src/registry-client.ts → PluginRegistryClient
packages/registry/src/integrity.ts  → verifyBundle()
themes/theme-blog/src/index.ts      → blogTheme() factory
themes/theme-insurance/src/index.ts → insuranceTheme() factory
themes/theme-insurance/src/companion-plugin.ts → insuranceCompanionPlugin() — home carousel schema, THEME_BEFORE_RENDER hook, HomeCarouselView admin UI
plugins/plugin-menu/src/index.ts    → menuPlugin() factory — menu + menu_items schema, THEME_BEFORE_RENDER hook injects menuMain/menuFooter, MenusView admin UI
apps/admin/src/main.ts              → dynamic plugin route registration via import()
apps/admin/src/composables/usePluginManifest.ts → fetch + cache plugin manifest from API
```

